nodes.text: 2010 Topps Star Wars: The Clone Wars Rise of the Bounty Hunters

2010 Topps Star Wars: The Clone Wars Rise of the Bounty Hunters is a trading card set released by Topps in 2010. It was based on season two of the television series Star Wars: The Clone Wars, which was marketed under the name "Rise of the Bounty Hunters." The base set contains 90 cards and was advertised as having four cards from each episode of the season.
